      <section id="failures" class="card">
        <h2>Failure modes</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Accessibility tree incomplete:</strong> action: ensure the page is in the right state before snapshot.</li>
          <li><strong>Multiple elements share role/name:</strong> action: annotate ambiguity and suggest stronger semantic anchor.</li>
          <li><strong>Team falls back to CSS anyway:</strong> action: preserve risk labels and policy note.</li>
          <li><strong>Dynamic content makes text unstable:</strong> action: parameterize test data or favor role+label on controls.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

